Package edu.cornell.gdiac.json.gum

Class GumJointPair

java.lang.Object
edu.cornell.gdiac.json.gum.GumJointPair
public class GumJointPair extends Object
Represents a tuple of a Bubblegum object and the joint it created when it collided with a body. The joint is either a Joint or JointDef object.
